HEADWORD: anomalops
<hw>anomalops</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fr>1</fr> <def>a fish having a
luminous organ beneath eye; it inhabits warm waters of the West Pacific
and Puerto Rico. It is called also <altname>flashlight
fish</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> flashlight fish</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

